{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/return-part-of-an-array-using-the-slice-method","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"functional-programming","demoType":null,"title":"Vrati deo niza podataka koristeći `slice` metod","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Funkcija <code>slice</code> vraća kopiju određenih elemenata niza podataka. Može prihvatiti dva argumenta: prvi navodi indeks za početak sečenja, a drugi indeks za kraj sečenja (ne uključujući). Ako nisu navedeni argumenti, podrazumevano je da počinje od početka niza podataka do kraja, što je jednostavan način za kreiranje kopije celog niza. Funkcija <code>slice</code> ne modifikuje originalni niz podataka, već vraća novi.</p>\n<p>Evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const arr = [\"Cat\", \"Dog\", \"Tiger\", \"Zebra\"];\r\nconst newArray = arr.slice(1, 3);\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>newArray</code> ima vrednost <code>[\"Dog\", \"Tiger\"]</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7b90367417b2b2512b65","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristi putanju <code>slice</code> u funkciji <code>sliceArray</code> da vrati deo redova podataka iz <code>anim</code> uzimajući u obzir indikatore <code>beginSlice</code> i <code>endSlice</code> koji su dati. Funkcija treba da vrati redove podataka.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301239,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/return-part-of-an-array-using-the-slice-method"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function sliceArray(anim, beginSlice, endSlice) {\r\n  // Only change code below this line\r\n\r\n\r\n  // Only change code above this line\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst inputAnim = [\"Cat\", \"Dog\", \"Tiger\", \"Zebra\", \"Ant\"];\r\nsliceArray(inputAnim, 1, 3);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Tvoj kod bi trebalo da koristi metod <code>slice</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/\\.slice/g));"},{"text":"<p>Parametar za <code>inputAnim</code> se ne sme menjati.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  JSON.stringify(inputAnim) ===\r\n    JSON.stringify(['Cat', 'Dog', 'Tiger', 'Zebra', 'Ant'])\r\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>sliceArray([\"Cat\", \"Dog\", \"Tiger\", \"Zebra\", \"Ant\"], 1, 3)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>[\"Dog\", \"Tiger\"]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  JSON.stringify(sliceArray(['Cat', 'Dog', 'Tiger', 'Zebra', 'Ant'], 1, 3)) ===\r\n    JSON.stringify(['Dog', 'Tiger'])\r\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>sliceArray([\"Cat\", \"Dog\", \"Tiger\", \"Zebra\", \"Ant\"], 0, 1)</code> treba da vrati <code>[\"Cat\"]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  JSON.stringify(sliceArray(['Cat', 'Dog', 'Tiger', 'Zebra', 'Ant'], 0, 1)) ===\r\n    JSON.stringify(['Cat'])\r\n);"},{"text":"<p><code>sliceArray([\"Cat\", \"Dog\", \"Tiger\", \"Zebra\", \"Ant\"], 1, 4)</code> treba da vrati <code>[\"Dog\", \"Tiger\", \"Zebra\"]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  JSON.stringify(sliceArray(['Cat', 'Dog', 'Tiger', 'Zebra', 'Ant'], 1, 4)) ===\r\n    JSON.stringify(['Dog', 'Tiger', 'Zebra'])\r\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#functional-programming","dashedName":"return-part-of-an-array-using-the-slice-method","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"functional-programming","isFirstSte